<h1>BA (Hons) Criminological Studies</h1>

											
																
		
		
		



		
			<span class="h4_red">UCAS Code:</span> M930 BA/CS<br />	
		
			<span class="h4_red">Duration:</span> Four years full-time.<br />	
		
			<span class="h4_red">Number of Places:</span> Approx. 40.<br />	
<br />
		
			<a href="#Intro">Introduction</a><br />	
		
			<a href="#Themes">Core Themes</a><br />	
		
			<a href="#Career">Career Opportunities</a><br />	
		
			
					
			
					
			
					
			
			
			
			
			
			
			
					
			
					
			
					
